FBIS4-54485 "dreeu084_i_94022" FBIS-EEU-94-084 Daily Report 1 May 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA One Killed, Three Wounded in Tuzla Shelling One Killed, Three Wounded in Tuzla Shelling LD0105203894 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 2000 GMT 1 May 94 LD0105203894 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpt] The chetniks today showed us yet again in the most brutal way that, as far as they were concerned, no UN decisions on protected areas in Bosnia-Herzegovina had any validity. Between 1500 and 1600 GMT this afternoon they fired several artillery shells on Tuzla. This attack against civilian targets caused fresh casualties: One 22-year-old girl was killed, one person seriously, and three lightly wounded. [passage omitted]
